purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to breast cancer.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes primary and secondary breast cancer as well as cancer metastatic to the breasts.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes benign neoplasms, carcinoma in situ, breast neoplasms of uncertain behavior, breast cancer in remission, personal and/or family history of breast cancer, and complications due to breast cancer.)
